    "chunk_id": "carrier_hi_wall_qhf_series_1434506032_p47_c12_510834",
    "text": "Index2: \n1: Indoor AC Fan Motor \nPower on and set the unit running in fan mode at high fan speed. After running for 15 seconds, \nmeasure the voltage of pin1 and pin2. If the value of the voltage is less than 100V(208~240V power \nsupply)or 50V(115V power supply), the PCB must has problems and need to be replaced.",
    "token_count": 86,
    "metadata": {
